		<div class="elementor-element elementor-element-175919b8 e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent" data-id="175919b8" data-element_type="container">
					<div class="e-con-inner">
				<div class="elementor-element elementor-element-3f24a526 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor" data-id="3f24a526" data-element_type="widget" data-widget_type="text-editor.default">
				<div class="elementor-widget-container">
									<p>Matteo Busso, who teaches DataScientia&#8217;s course on AI in Everyday Life at the University of Trento, shared his insights in a recent interview for the Master in Communication of Science and Innovation (Scicomm) program there. He highlighted the crucial role of education in navigating AI&#8217;s transformative impacts on science, research, and society. Through his work at DataScientia, Matteo advocates for the importance of education in shaping AI&#8217;s future and ensuring its responsible application in science and communication.</p>								</div>
				</div>
				<div class="elementor-element elementor-element-461bc401 elementor-widget-divider--view-line elementor-widget elementor-widget-divider" data-id="461bc401" data-element_type="widget" data-widget_type="divider.default">
				<div class="elementor-widget-container">
							<div class="elementor-divider">
			<span class="elementor-divider-separator">
						</span>
		</div>
						</div>
				</div>
					</div>
				</div>
		<div class="elementor-element elementor-element-3c4a8e70 e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent" data-id="3c4a8e70" data-element_type="container">
					<div class="e-con-inner">
				<div class="elementor-element elementor-element-5123e894 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor" data-id="5123e894" data-element_type="widget" data-widget_type="text-editor.default">
				<div class="elementor-widget-container">
									<p>&nbsp;In the interview, Matteo explored how AI is reshaping the landscape of science communication and research. He discussed how AI enhances the accessibility of scientific content, supports data-driven insights, which enables more dynamic engagement. However, Matteo also stressed that AI’s potential can only be realized through proper education. He highlighted how critical it is to understand AI’s limitations, avoid misinformation, and address the growing “AI divide” among nations thta lead tech and that lack resources. He stresses that unequal access to computational resources hinders global participation. As someone who works for <span data-start="958" data-end="974">DataScientia</span>, Matteo is committed to ensuring that education is at the heart of AI development, preparing future generations to not only use AI effectively but also to think critically about its applications.</p>								</div>
				</div>
				<div class="elementor-element elementor-element-172ea55c elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor" data-id="172ea55c" data-element_type="widget" data-widget_type="text-editor.default">
				<div class="elementor-widget-container">
									<p>Matteo’s insights are part of a broader global conversation about AI’s influence on scientific fields such as climate science, healthcare, and data-driven research. His role at <span data-start="1360" data-end="1376">DataScientia</span> is directly tied to this conversation, as the organization is dedicated to advancing AI education. By fostering an understanding of AI across all levels, <span data-start="1531" data-end="1547">DataScientia</span> helps ensure that AI is used responsibly and that diverse communities are included in the development and application of this transformative technology.</p><p>AI is revolutionizing scientific work, but with these advancements come significant challenges. Matteo emphasizes the importance of education to prepare future AI professionals to understand AI’s nuances, its ethical implications, and its potential to address global challenges. Education is key to ensuring that AI serves diverse communities equitably and responsibly. At <span data-start="2099" data-end="2115">DataScientia</span>, the belief is that empowering individuals with the knowledge and skills to create, manage, and apply AI in an informed way is essential for overcoming these challenges and ensuring AI’s benefits are accessible to everyone.</p>								</div>
				</div>
				<div class="elementor-element elementor-element-6e409d3 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor" data-id="6e409d3" data-element_type="widget" data-widget_type="text-editor.default">
